    <section class="flexibleblocks-block __text __animate __smlmargin">
        <div class="container-fluid">
            <div class="row __center">
                <div class="col-12 col-lg-8 col-xl-6">
                    <div class="usercontent">
                        <p>The Welsh Language Standards (No.3) Regulations 2016 were not approved. They were re-submitted and approved as No.6 Regulations on 31 January, 2017.</p>
<p><strong>Imposing standards</strong></p>
<p>The Commissioner is responsible for imposing standards on organisations. He does so by giving a ‘compliance notice’ to them. It is a legal document that lists the standards that an organisation is required to comply with. The Commissioner consults with each organisation before giving them their compliance notice.  </p>
<p><strong>Enforcing standards</strong></p>
<p>The final statutory step in relation to the standards regime is to ensure that the requirements of a compliance notice are complied with. This will be done by enforcing standards.  </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>


